            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ari</ex></expan> divi Sep<lb break="no" n="2"/>timii Severi Pii <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>Arab</abbr><ex>ici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Adiab</abbr><ex>enici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Part</abbr><ex>hici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>annici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imi</ex></expan> filio divi <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Antonini Pii <expan><abbr>Ger</abbr><ex>manici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Sarm</abbr><ex>atici</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>nepoti divi Antonini <lb n="7"/>Pii pronepoti divi Hadria<lb break="no" n="8"/>ni abnepoti divi Traia<lb break="no" n="9"/>ni <expan><abbr>Part</abbr><ex>hici</ex></expan> et divi Nervae <lb n="10"/>adnepoti <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arco</ex></expan> Aurelio Antonino <lb n="12"/>Pio <expan><abbr>Aug</abbr><ex>usto</ex></expan> <lb n="13"/><expan><abbr>Parthic</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Brit</abbr><ex>annico</ex></expan> <lb n="14"/><expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pont</abbr><ex>ifici</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>max</abbr><ex>imo</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>trib</abbr><ex>unicia</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pot</abbr><ex>estate</ex></expan> <lb n="15"/>XV <expan><abbr>imp</abbr><ex>eratori</ex></expan> bis co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> IIII <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>atriae</ex></expan> <lb n="16"/>pacatori orbis <lb n="17"/>res <expan><abbr>pub</abbr><ex>lica</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Tuccitanor</abbr><ex>um</ex></expan> <lb n="18"/><expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecreto</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ecurionum</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Der Text ist heute in weiten Teilen nicht mehr lesbar. (B): CIL II 1671: Z. 3: ADIB. Datierung: nach der trib. pot. zwischen 10.12.211 und 9.12.212; allerdings war Caracalla erst im Jahr 213 zum 4. Mal Konsul. Im Text müßte also entweder trib. pot. XV&amp;lt;I&amp;gt; oder cos. III{I} korrigiert werden.</p>
            </div>
